            for creating web pages
          </dd>

          <dt>CSS3</dt>
          <dd>
            Cascading Style Sheets version 3 - used for styling and layout of
            web pages
          </dd>

          <dt>JavaScript</dt>
          <dd>
            A programming language that adds interactivity and dynamic behavior
            to web pages
          </dd>
